steps.html_instructions: N 49th St turns slightly right and becomes Jonah St

Take exit 8C to merge onto US-61 N toward Natchez
Entering Mississippi

Turn left onto US-425 N/John R Junkin Dr
Continue to follow US-425 N
Entering Louisiana

Turn left onto LA-2 W/US-165 S/US-425 N/Mer Rouge Rd
Continue to follow LA-2 W/US-165 S/US-425 N
Keep left at the fork and merge onto I-530 N
Take exit 2B for Doctor Martin Luther King Junior Drive

Turn right onto Dr Martin Luther King Dr/M L King (signs for State Capitol Complex)
Continue to follow Dr Martin Luther King Dr
